            ";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:12:"长泽雅美";}s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Fri, 11 Sep 2015 18:00:00 +0800";s:4:"guid";s:54:"http://www.zhihu.com/question/26802404/answer/61422482";s:7:"summary";s:3049:"这个是经济学里，尤其是微观经济学需求理论里经常碰到的Berge's maximum theorem的推论：<br><br><b>Berge's maximum theorem：</b>给定一个带参数的最优化问题<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cmax_%7Bz+%5Cin+A%28%5Ctheta%29+%7DF%28z%2C+%5Ctheta%29" alt="\max_{z \in A(\theta) }F(z, \theta)" eeimg="1"><br>满足：<br><ol><li>多值函数<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Ctheta+%5CRightarrow+A%28%5Ctheta%29" alt="\theta \Rightarrow A(\theta)" eeimg="1"> 是连续的，且<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%28%5Ctheta%29" alt="A(\theta)" eeimg="1">是紧致的。<br></li><li>函数<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=%28z%2C+%5Ctheta%29+%5Cmapsto+F%28z%2C+%5Ctheta%29+" alt="(z, \theta) \mapsto F(z, \theta) " eeimg="1">是连续的<br></li></ol>则<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Ctheta+%5Cmapsto+%5Cmax_%7Bz+%5Cin+A%28%5Ctheta%29+%7DF%28z%2C+%5Ctheta%29" alt="\theta \mapsto \max_{z \in A(\theta) }F(z, \theta)" eeimg="1">是连续的，而多值函数<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Ctheta+++%5CRightarrow+%5Coperatorname%7Bargmax%7D_%7BA%28%5Ctheta%29%7DF%28%5Ccdot%2C+%5Ctheta%29" alt="\theta   \Rightarrow \operatorname{argmax}_{A(\theta)}F(\cdot, \theta)" eeimg="1">是上半连续的<br><br>这里<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Ctheta" alt="\theta" eeimg="1">对应其他人选择的策略<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Csigma_%7B-i%7D" alt="\sigma_{-i}" eeimg="1">, 而<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=A%28%5Ctheta%29+%3D+%E3%80%81%28A_i%29" alt="A(\theta) = 、(A_i)" eeimg="1">对应一个常多值函数。<br>所以<img src="//zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Csigma_%7B-i%7D+++%5CRightarrow+%5Coperatorname%7Bargmax%7D_%7B%E3%80%81%28A_i%29%7Du_i%28%5Ccdot%2C+%5Csigma_%7B-i%7D+%29" alt="\sigma_{-i}   \Rightarrow \operatorname{argmax}_{、(A_i)}u_i(\cdot, \sigma_{-i} )" eeimg="1">是上半连续的。
